 **CLIENT_ACKNOWLEDGE**   
With this acknowledgment mode, the client acknowledges a consumed message by calling the message&#39;s acknowledge method.   

    Session session = connection.createSession(false, Session.CLIENT_ACKNOWLEDGE);
    ...
    msg = (TextMessage) consumer.receive();
    //acknowledge
