 **AUTO_ACKNOWLEDGE**   
With this acknowledgment mode, the session automatically acknowledges a client&#39;s receipt of a message either when the session has successfully returned from a call to receive or when the message listener the session has called to process the message successfully returns.  

    Session session = connection.createSession(false,Session.AUTO_ACKNOWLEDGE);

